{
  "text": "Using the concept of μ−eccentric nodes, in (Sunitha and Vijayakumar 1998) Sunitha and Vijayakumar has proved the sufficient conditions for a fuzzy graph G such that G * is a cycle to be self centered. In this section, sufficient conditions for a cycle to be self centered based on strong sum distance are discussed. Note that all arcs in a fuzzy cycle are strong [CITATION_1] ).",
